  "title": "Architectural Coordinator",
  "description": "<ul><li>Review architectural drawings, specifications, and other design documentation to identify and resolve any issues or conflicts.</li><li>Ensure all architectural work complies with relevant building codes, regulations, and company standards.</li><li>Facilitate regular progress meetings with the design team and provide updates on the status of architectural deliverables.</li><li>Collaborate closely with project architects, engineers, and other stakeholders to coordinate the architectural design and planning of construction projects.</li><li>Support the implementation of architectural design solutions on site, working closely with the construction team.</li><li>Contribute to the continuous improvement of architectural coordination processes and documentation.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
